                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-6 text-center less-paddings">
                <div class="panel panel-success">
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        <h3>Map: Deikstra's algorythm</h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-3 col-xs-3">
                Aim: defeat your enemy.
                Maybe here will be a minimap.
            </div>
        </header>
        <div id="canva"></div>
        <footer class="bounded-block">
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-3 col-xs-3 less-paddings scrollable-block">
                <ul class="list-group">
                    <li class="list-group-item bot-item active" id="botList0">Bot1</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item bot-item" id="botList1">Bot2</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item bot-item" id="botList2">Bot3</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item bot-item" id="botList3">Bot4</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-6 height-100 less-paddings">
                <textarea class="form-control height-100" id="code"></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-3 col-xs-3 panel-group less-paddings scrollable-block">
                <div class="panel panel-danger">
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        Control panel
                        <div class="pull-right compile-buttons-block">
                            <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Compile</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Run</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="clearfix"></div>
                    <div class="panel-body">
